    NinjaTrader Desktop Connection Guides

    This is a repository of guides for connecting to accounts and data feeds outside of NinjaTrader

    Last Reviewed
    15/07/2024
    Last Published
    18/12/2024

    Below is a full list of connection guides for supported connection types in the NinjaTrader Desktop app: 

    • NinjaTrader Brokerage Accounts
    • NinjaTrader Continuum (for use with previous versions of NinjaTrader Desktop)
    • Barchart
    • Coinbase
    • cTrader
    • eSignal
    • Forex.com / City Index
    • FXCM
    • IQFeed
    • Kinetick
    • Interactive Brokers
    • Rithmic
    • Schwab (beta)
    • Rithmic Evaluation Service
    • Tradovate Evaluation Service
